1. Product Overview

Product Name

TechPath

Product Summary

TechPath is an all-in-one Georgia Tech course information and planning platform that allows students to search for courses, evaluate instructors, read reviews, build semester schedules, and plan their full academic career.

The platform combines the functionality of:

• Course search
• Instructor insights
• Student reviews
• Schedule builder
• Academic career planner
• Administrative course database management

The system enforces strict relational database integrity and structured object assignment. Any relational entity such as instructors, courses, or prerequisites must be selected from existing records rather than manually typed.

⸻

2. Product Goals

Primary Goals

Provide Georgia Tech students with a single platform where they can:

• Discover courses
• Evaluate instructors
• Build semester schedules
• Plan their entire academic career

⸻

Secondary Goals

